## Purple Cow

Purple cow is a book written by seth Godin, well known marketing guru and best selling author.
Godin urges everyone involved in creating, desigining or selling to think in new ways about their market.
Godin argues that by adopting remarkability as a core differentiator the world's best companies have built incredibly viral 
products.